elements.name: A user searches a product (hat) and add it to the cart

steps.name: I am on the Amazon Home page
I Search for hats with the category "Hats" in the products search field
I select the first product on the "RESULTS" page
I select quantity 2 for the selected product
I add the product to the cart
I open the cart to continue with the purchase
